Home Brewers Gold

By Charlie Papazian

Home Brewer's Gold features over 100 All Grain and Malt extract recipes to help you make these prize-winning beers at home. 
 
In 1996 the brewers of the world met the ultimate challenge: the World Beer Cup International Competition. Only the most magnificent examples of the brewmaster's art qualified for the top award: the Gold Cup.
